# --- Contact form ---
# 1) Create a free access key at https://web3forms.com (set delivery email to yours).
# 2) In THIS folder (next to package.json), edit `.env.local` and paste the key on ONE line:
#
#    NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=paste_your_key_here
#
#    (No quotes. No spaces around =. The value must not be empty.)
# 3) Stop and restart `npm run dev` so Next.js picks up the variable.
#
# Optional: same key without NEXT_PUBLIC_ for server-only sending via /api/contact:
# WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=paste_your_key_here
#
# Optional: Resend — https://resend.com
# RESEND_API_KEY=
# CONTACT_TO_EMAIL=earlbalitcha@gmail.com
# CONTACT_FROM_EMAIL=Portfolio <onboarding@resend.dev>
